<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 15. Hypermastus sp., Tel Aviv, Israel, HELM project (sample S 67 _ 3 F): front (A, B), side (C, D) and back (E) views, apex with optical microscope (F) and SEM (G) showing the protoconch-teleoconch transition (the shell had a different orientation in images F and G). The arrow marks the constriction between protoconch and teleoconch that is a diagnostic character for this species. Scale bars: 0.5 mm (A-E); 0.2 mm (F, G)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/496968" .

